{"tid":696246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"座駕遭兩車夾擊　逃跑百米中刀 新義安內訌　頭目生日捱斬命危","createTime":"2018-06-10T02:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T03:37:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a9850862e840c548fc64e98ef0cbe1f69bfaa5b1","tid":696246,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180610/20416129\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180610%2F20416129&d=OzmwPigTyqvMq9bLATKCME4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=97475f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180610%2F20416129&h=d3ef701b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180610/20416129</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月10日 <br />\n<br />\n座駕遭兩車夾擊　逃跑百米中刀<br />\n新義安內訌　頭目生日捱斬命危<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180610/large/10la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180610%2Flarge%2F10la8p11.jpg&h=04a0637b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■傷者手腳及背中多刀，送院情況危殆。江寶龍攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名新義安小頭目，昨凌晨乘友人駕駛的平治房車往紅磡慶生時遭多名刀手伏擊，他街頭狂奔100米仍被追及圍斬，手腳背中12刀重創，倒卧血泊不省人事，經送院後性命垂危。刀手逞兇後跳回接應車輛逃去無蹤，警方事後在葵涌尋回其中一輛涉案七人車，已遭人縱火燒車滅證，警方將案件列傷人跟進，初步不排除是黑幫同門因金錢利益內訌肇禍。<br />\n<br />\n記者：唐家輝　梁澤岡　江寶龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭亂刀斬傷的男子姓潘（40歲），據悉為屯門新義安小頭目，綽號「肥東」，報稱經營汽車美容生意。消息稱，潘早前因養魚塘生意問題，與另一名同門小頭目「家熙」發生爭拗，並向對方追收一筆過百萬元金額的債務，對方親屬其後莫名遇襲。而剛巧今日是潘41歲生辰，懷疑有人處心積慮報復「贈興」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180610/large/10la8p12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180610%2Flarge%2F10la8p12.jpg&h=8a2f6498&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事平治車頭損毀，警員封鎖現場調查。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180610/large/a0801a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180610%2Flarge%2Fa0801a.gif&h=4e4fe6ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨日凌晨零時許，潘乘坐姓鄭男友人（38歲）駕駛的平治，沿紅磡寶其利街行駛，擬出外慶生，平治駛至近黃埔街交界時，一輛私家車突從左邊切入，在車頭「閘停」平治及撞甩平治泵把，另一輛七人車則從後撞平治車尾，平治上兩人見勢色不對，先後開車門逃跑，鄭沿車尾狂奔，潘則往黃埔街方向逃走。<br />\n<br />\n而對方兩車上數名戴上口罩、持開山刀的刀手立即跳車追截，潘沿黃埔街暴走100米，至近必嘉街交界被其中三名刀手追及揮刀狂斬，手腳背至少中12刀受創，起初仍有氣力呼救，其後倒卧血泊昏迷不醒。涉案刀手完事即跳上兩車，倒車沿機利士南路逃離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉案七人車被焚毀<br />\n<br />\n警方聞訊封鎖涉事路段調查，安排傷者送院，潘經搶救後情況危殆，現場遺下一大灘血迹，路邊有事主留下的波鞋及刀手棄下的刀套。事後約19分鐘，一輛豐田Picnic七人車於葵涌貨櫃碼頭南路近呈祥道一個露天停車場對開起火，消防到場救熄火勢，在車廂尋獲一個天拿水罐，認為起火原因有可疑，警方初步相信該七人車與紅磡斬人案有關，經調查獲悉是報失車輛，被人套上假牌犯案，案件交由九龍城重案組跟進，正追緝三名在逃的中國籍刀手。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n劏牛掛屍案　PTU大帽山緝兇<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n同門「家樂」鬥「鮑魚」"},{"pid":"cd1d3ec84e9ba2cd8afff4bc44fee0e009c8fd61","tid":696246,"uid":161731,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"家樂鬥鮑魚又係咩玩法"},{"pid":"117f210593c8013ae57b271d3de6aa04102e78eb","tid":696246,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:30:51.000Z","msg":"40定41歲"},{"pid":"46bcb1c34748800cc8fc4cf3b5b9bc7c88d079ae","tid":696246,"uid":115415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd1d3ec84e9ba2cd8afff4bc44fee0e009c8fd61","tid":696246,"uid":161731,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:29:39.000Z","msg":"家樂鬥鮑魚又係咩玩法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"唔講以為開酒樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又生菜又鮑魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090eb3c99ad505858e76d893c501243be8f0ddb1","tid":696246,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:34:42.000Z","msg":"以死相搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd4a656dc92e83c734ad4a3cc68bfcfd5a6bc75","tid":696246,"uid":12058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"油麻they<br />\n沙田me"},{"pid":"202c49bb4618fb00e1ed4156bb82af0be7e28bfe","tid":696246,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"終於唔係食物名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb1d8ab395bf136551f39db83894b9a361386a0","tid":696246,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7591290b954a0d77d22d860afde11c9577a1085","tid":696246,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"正常名"},{"pid":"2d3cb777789592cbb5048eb7b5ee031b2bd175ba","tid":696246,"uid":161935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:36:19.000Z","msg":"以為有新點心睇"},{"pid":"d423ab01de0a4e42d68dc2bde0dade15b8d141e4","tid":696246,"uid":102132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}